	//    - `indent` (int): Indentation spacing for nested objects (default: 2)
	//    - `delimiter` (string): Field separator for tabular arrays (default: none, use `"\t"` for tabs)
	//
	//    **Example output:**
	//    ```
	//    title: Introduction to Vector Search
	//    author: Jane Doe
